caption: It is this church that hosts conferences to promote the death ritual of Spanish bullfighting?? It is a crime, the law no longer authorizes abuse and cruelty carried out on animals for pleasure and spectacle! Why does the Church authorize such a conference?? This is absolutely outrageous!
